SIMPLE: diffusible
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diffusible
<hw>Dif*fu"si*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Capable of flowing or spreading in all directions; that may be
diffused.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Capable of passing through
animal membranes by osmosis.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diffusibleness</ent>⟦br⟧
